{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/understanding-undefined-value-returned-from-a-function","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-javascript","demoType":null,"title":"Razumevanje undefined Vrednosti Koju Funkcija Vraca","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Funkcija moze da sadrzi <code>return</code> iskaz, ali ne mora. Kada funkcija nema <code>return</code>, pri pozivu izvrsava unutrasnji kod, ali vracena vrednost je <code>undefined</code>.</p>\n<p><strong>Primer</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">let sum = 0;\n\nfunction addSum(num) {\n  sum = sum + num;\n}\n\naddSum(3);\n</code></pre>\n<p><code>addSum</code> je funkcija bez <code>return</code> iskaza. Funkcija menja globalnu promenljivu <code>sum</code>, ali njena povratna vrednost je <code>undefined</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"598e8944f009e646fc236146","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Napravite funkciju <code>addFive</code> bez argumenata. Ova funkcija treba da doda 5 promenljivoj <code>sum</code>, ali povratna vrednost treba da bude <code>undefined</code>.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301177,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/understanding-undefined-value-returned-from-a-function"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"// Setup\nlet sum = 0;\n\nfunction addThree() {\n  sum = sum + 3;\n}\n\n// Only change code below this line\n\n\n// Only change code above this line\n\naddThree();\naddFive();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tes